&lt;div class=&quot;input-box&quot;&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;waffle-rich-text-editor&quot; class=&quot;cell-input editable disabled-input&quot;&gt;The Business Systems team defines and builds the business IT architecture that supports the commercial operation of Waymo&#39;s autonomous fleet. The team stands at the intersection of finance, operations and IT; through creative architecture, expertise and attention to detail, it ensures that Waymo has world-class capabilities across all its business processes.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;In this hybrid role, you will report to Manager Network Engineering&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Design &amp;amp; Implementation:&lt;/strong&gt; Design and implement multi-quarter network security projects across large-scale WiFi environments and data centers, driving outcomes as a key contributor and subject matter expert from concept through deployment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Production Network Design &amp;amp; Planning:&lt;/strong&gt; Create and review Engineering Design Plans (EDPs) for sites, collaborating closely with the greater Waymo network team to design overarching architectures that align with company security and design guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Excellence &amp;amp; Automation: &lt;/strong&gt;Proactively monitor production network performance to triage issues, building new processes and tools to scale systems while aligning on shared objectives with the broader networking discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Framework Development &amp;amp; Procedure Oversight: &lt;/strong&gt;Establish comprehensive security frameworks, standards, policies, and baselines across diverse network environments to bolster security posture, optimize performance, and mitigate operational risks. Create and maintain Method of Procedures (MOPs) to provide clear guidance for internal teams and external partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Threat Modeling &amp;amp; Assessments: &lt;/strong&gt;Perform proactive security evaluations and threat modeling for network infrastructure, products, and services. Work in close partnership with the broader Waymo network and cross-functional teams to coordinate resources and provide technical and non-technical stakeholders with actionable strategies for risk mitigation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Leadership &amp;amp; Regional Site Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the primary technical owner for network sites within a designated market territory, maintaining a consistent physical presence at field locations and the operations center. Responsible for establishing new sites, managing colocation data center racks, and providing hands-on support. Collaborate with Product, Operations, Facilities Management, and external partners to coordinate resources and deliver robust network security outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Computer Science, Engineering, a related field, or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10 years of experience with network routing protocols, design, and troubleshooting with network equipment providers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of hands-on experience designing, implementing, and securing large-scale datacenter environments and enterprise networks (LAN, WAN, WLAN, WiFi).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to act as a subject matter expert in network capacity planning, security principles, and infrastructure management best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience installing and troubleshooting wireless and/or optical networks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We prefer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with planning and designing complex, large-scale networks encompassing multiple sites and products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in network security engineering, security assessment, vulnerability management, and threat modeling to deliver organization-wide security programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to work with and influence cross-functional teams with similar objectives to align resources and drive positive security outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience developing architectural patterns with several reusable components to drive security at scale in enterprise environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with network automation tools in a CI/CD environment (e.g., Terraform, Ansible, Python).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to independently determine the optimal approach to solving deep and ambiguous technical network problems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a team-oriented, collaborative environment using Google workspace tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Yes; ability to travel to sites within operational responsibilities region and outside to new metro sites ( 25-30%)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The expected base salary range for this full-time position across US locations is listed below. Actual starting pay will be based on job-related factors, including exact work location, experience, relevant training and education, and skill level. Your recruiter can share more about the specific salary range for the role location or, if the role can be performed remote, the specific salary range for your preferred location, during the hiring process.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Waymo employees are also eligible to participate in Waymo’s discretionary annual bonus program, equity incentive plan, and generous Company benefits program, subject to eligibility requirements.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Salary Range&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$175,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$215,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DRW&lt;/strong&gt; is a diversified trading firm with over 3 decades of experience bringing sophisticated technology and exceptional people together to operate in markets around the world. We value autonomy and the ability to quickly pivot to capture opportunities, so we operate using our own capital and trading at our own risk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Headquartered in Chicago with offices throughout the U.S., Canada, Europe, and Asia, we trade a variety of asset classes including Fixed Income, ETFs, Equities, FX, Commodities and Energy across all major global markets. We have also leveraged our expertise and technology to expand into three non-traditional strategies: real estate, venture capital and cryptoassets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We operate with respect, curiosity and open minds. The people who thrive here share our belief that it’s not just what we do that matters–it&#39;s how we do it. &lt;strong&gt;DRW&lt;/strong&gt; is a place of high expectations, integrity, innovation and a willingness to challenge consensus.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are seeking a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Client Platforms Security Engineer &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;to work with the members of the security team to ensure that our client platform&amp;nbsp;infrastructure, virtual or physical, is properly&amp;nbsp;protected. You will engineer, maintain and implement security controls, audit configurations in a hybrid compute environment. You will generally ensure we are reducing risk footprint across the infrastructure without impacting its effectiveness. A successful candidate will have an attention to detail, the ability to understand what impact their changes will have on&amp;nbsp;the business teams and the services they use. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;What you’ll be doing:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;3&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Maintain security tools and their associated configurations &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;3&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;2&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Manage and coordinate updates of tools when new versions are released &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
